<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.8.2">
<l>ventiṟal vīraril vīraroppār vētamu raittimai yōrvaṇaṅkum</l>
<l>centamiḻ pāṭuvār tāmvaṇaṅkun tēvari varkolte rikkamāṭṭēṉ</l>
<l>vantuku ṟaḷuru vāynimirntu māvali vēḷviyil maṇṇaḷanta</l>
<l>vantaṇar pōṉṟiva rārkkoleṉṉa</l>
<l>vaṭṭapu yakarat tēṉeṉṟārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is the trustworthy one the hero among fierce, valiant heroes,</l>
<l rend="indent">the [same] god praised by celestials chanting the Vedas</l>
<l>And praised by those who sing in fine Tamil? I am not able to explain [it]!</l>
<l>When I asked, “Who is this who measured the earth,</l>
<l rend="indent">having appeared as a brahmin at Māvali’s sacrifice,</l>
<l rend="indent">coming in the form of a dwarf, then stretching?”</l>
<l>He answered, “I am he in the house of the eight-armed [lord].”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
